        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>PDMPs Help Patients Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) to establish a grant program to test the feasibility of integrating substance use disorder and behavioral health treatment locator tools into prescription drug monitoring programs. HHS may award grants to up to five states.</p>]]>
        </text>
